</title>
<subSubSection id="C5979ECCD64C7755CCCCD786FD59E842" pageId="null" pageNumber="358" type="description">
<paragraph id="C3D24AF60434379E7972F893719C67BC" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
<emphasis id="E3D86407F1D0BD54DEEB9D3A538095A0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
6-15 cm hoch. 
<normalizedToken id="4A0CD67916E66E2F5457AAF9BB4B91BD" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
0, 5-0,7 mm dick, mit 7 Nerven und 3 dicken 
<normalizedToken id="B02DF84B2593FBA3690D8EDF38563BD1" originalValue="Strängen" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Straengen</normalizedToken>
von Festigungsgewebe. 
<normalizedToken id="C49732EBE8AD942478708657BBB3CCD5" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(Traube oder Rispe) 
<emphasis id="4DCFB778F4D3BDEB37F1D61FB5ACAE6E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">1,5-3 cm lang.</emphasis>
Obere 
<normalizedToken id="CFECBACA9AD81C76ED7DA117C68072C2" originalValue="Hüllspelze" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Huellspelze</normalizedToken>
3,5-4,5 mm 
<pageBreakToken id="BCCD40C6E7929641BBECFE8453EF074F" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">lang</pageBreakToken>
. Deckspelzen begrannt; 
<emphasis id="AB5310F8423CCC50DA3465E32E6E3D95" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Granne mehr als</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="ACF5088D67E399979973848032258CA2" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="9C67A00B17A85C64D50D175B79077ED0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="2B3A256FC0BE2037C76F721544AC9751" originalValue="zugehörige" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">zugehoerige</normalizedToken>
Spelze.
</emphasis>
Staubbeutel 2-2,5 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="8797DD8FE8695ACB4547F1F33FB59B4B" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AE8EF9E5CB77D338102FBA2717E012A6" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
<emphasis id="E2941222F3E5765C491EBCF4BB2A84D6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 14:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="49299B2E18BC50050A204366B3876E31" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="65BAA775A3469C8FD632DB9D361D2AA7" originalValue="Stählin" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Staehlin</normalizedToken>
1929).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="034A16A5A231EADDDD2DD3EF7C151AF4" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
<emphasis id="21663D39C84092E7092B2F6DE4541988" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Saure, trockene, feinerdereiche, 
<normalizedToken id="A46DF67C519B595869D84E7C2EC7ECD8" originalValue="tiefgründige" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">tiefgruendige</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="DC4505E34FE5F4D4D9855C8FDB09C4C8" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Boeden</normalizedToken>
an steilen 
<normalizedToken id="6FEDA6D7EA9E4DF8A706F2475590F95D" originalValue="Hängen" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Haengen</normalizedToken>
mit kurzer Schneebedeckung (5-6 Monate). 
<taxonomicName id="DF942C61968CBF28A69C416B27A430F3" authority="Br." authorityName="Br." class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Festucetum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="358" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="halleri">
<emphasis id="9A239C4C24134DB54B838E8ECFD9CC96" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Festucetum Halleri</emphasis>
Br.
</taxonomicName>
-Bl. 1926.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="965943A8C9D3D20252E3B25741C1F94C" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
<emphasis id="7AF55CCBFDED48931831DAB44D150D63" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="A487013105B1124AE251CA735590E90E" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="C2D9CBE5A0B8BE3657F4640DD62BE9F2" originalValue="südlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">suedlich</normalizedToken>
): 
<normalizedToken id="5B1FC34D199613A6D10962A0238AA168" originalValue="Ostpyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="358">Ostpyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Mont Ventoux, Alpen, Korsika, Apennin, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel. - Im Gebiet: Alpen (Urgesteinsketten).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
